    				Services    			


Ramesh has been a very active member of professional communities in which he did research. He served on editorial/advisory boards of numerous magazines and journals. He also served in various capacities at many different conferences and workshops. His role in conferences have been from serving on Program Committees to serving as a General Chair.
The editorial boards he has served on includes:

ACM Transactions on Multimedia Computing, Communications, and Applications
Computer Vision Graphics and Image Processing
IEEE Intelligent Systems Magazine
IEEE Multimedia Magazine
IEEE Transactions on Multimedia
Journal of Optical Society
Machine Vision and Applications
Multimedia Systems
Multimedia Tools and Applications
Optical Engineering

The conferences he has been involved with includes:

ACM Multimedia
ACM Multimedia Information Retrieval
IEEE Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition
IEEE International Conference on Computer Vision
IEEE International Conference on Data Engineering
IEEE International Conference on Multimedia and Expo
Workshops on Motion Analysis














